msgid "(The street is clearly looping. There's little point in running around like this.)"
msgstr "(道路顯然在循環。繞著跑沒什麼意義。)"

msgid "A bus stop sign."
msgstr "公車站牌。"

msgid "The schedule is empty. It's likely that there's no next bus coming."
msgstr "時刻表是空的。顯然沒有下一班公車。"

msgid "A lamppost that makes this feel like a safe spot."
msgstr "讓這裡充滿安全感的燈柱。"

msgid "A crow standing on a rock."
msgstr "站在石頭上的烏鴉。"

msgid "It doesn't seem bothered by my presence."
msgstr "看起來牠不被我的存在所動。"

msgid "A trash can. It's overflowing with emptiness."
msgstr "垃圾桶。裝滿了空虛。"
